data.description: Check Out This Beautiful Home in Westfield with 1.88 acres Just Waiting for You! This Home Features an Open Floor Plan with 3 Spacious Bedrooms and 2 Full Baths. The Exposed Beam Ceilings, Rock Fireplace and Hardwood Flooring Throughout, Provide All of the Warmth and Coziness of a Mountain Chalet. Main Level Primary Bedroom with Private Deck. Upper Bedroom with Private Balcony which Overlooks the Expansive Yard. Enjoy Morning Coffee on the 14x10 Screened Porch or the 40x10 Front Deck Overlooking the Yard. There's Plenty of Storage with the 18x12 Workshop, the 10x8 Garden Shed and the 16x8 Equipment Shed. All of This and an Attached Carport. This Home Has So Much to Offer! Call Today!
